docs.text: Welcome to RustSmith Documentation! RustSmith is a randomized program fuzzer for the Rust programming language that will generate valid programs that excercise multiple parts of the Rust programming language, in an attempt to uncover bugs in Rust compilers. Check out the documentation below to get started and learn about all its features! Getting Started
